# AI Cost Guardian

## 🚀 Overview
AI system to detect and reduce enterprise cost leakage.

## 💡 Features
- Detect duplicate invoices
- Identify overpricing
- Suggest cost optimization
- Automated action recommendations

## 🧱 Tech Stack
